data.text: Welcome to March/May’s Issue of Influential People Magazine! We are excited you took time out of your precious day to read this amazing issue! The month of March focuses on International Women's Day! This annual award recognizes and celebrates women, in all their diversity, who have dedicated their lives to promoting human rights, gender equity and equality, peace, justice, the rule of law, and accountability – often at great personal risk or sacrifice. While May is the month celebrating and honoring the mother of a family or individual, as well as motherhood, maternal bonds, and the influence of mothers in society. And the month of May is the World Economic Forum that brings together communities of leaders around the world on global issues, such as the pandemic, climate change, food issues, schools, and technology.
